    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Oceanapia hechteli nom nov. (UFPEPOR 3172). A, preserved specimen; B, thick section showing ectosome and choanosome; C, oxeas. Scale bars: A = 3 cm; B = 1000 µm; C = 50 µm." ;
